commit.message:
Merge pull request #10 from jmagnusson/new-pid-suffix

Support gunicorn 19.6.0

rainbow-saddle support for gunicorn 19.6.0

rainbow-saddle 0.3.2 breaks with latest gunicorn version because pid is saved to a new file location since this commit https://github.com/benoitc/gunicorn/commit/418f140445c050af541abeb02835c6c78b2a71f0. (And now it’s the new pid instead of the old one).

Please note that this commit drops support for all previous versions of gunicorn. Supporting both is definitely possible, but I’m happy with supporting only the new better signal handling.
